Take The Freestyle with you anywhere and enjoy your favourite content on a big screen. Join Samsung's National Training Manager, Jeff Ingram for a Live Shopping event on August 2nd at 6PM EDT to learn more about our portable projector. There will also be special offer up for grabs. Don't miss out!
